---
// src/components/OfferingsGrid.astro
---
<section class="py-16 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">The Core Offerings</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Our approach focuses on proper protection, the power of choice, and long-term clarity. We help families from all walks of life make informed financial choices.
      </p>
    </div>

    <ul role="list" class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <li class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300 border border-gray-100">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Financial Education First</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Empowering you to understand how money works.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300 border border-gray-100">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Customized Strategy</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Utilizing a complimentary Financial Needs Analysis (FNA) to map your unique goals.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300 border border-gray-100">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Proper Protection</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Guarding your family's assets with access to a broad portfolio of industry-leading providers.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300 border border-gray-100">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Building & Preserving Wealth</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Long-term strategies designed to help outpace inflation and build a lasting family legacy.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
